onlyOwner: Ownable: caller is not the owner
onlyRoleManager: AccessControl: sender must be an admin to grant
swapExceedBalance: Swap amount is bigger than the balance
swapExceedAllowance: Swap amount is bigger than the allowance
tokenHolderOrOwner: Either the owner or a tokenholder can swapAllToken
toZeroAddress: ERC20: transfer to the zero address
engineNotStart: Upgrade has not started yet. Cannot reset the engine address!
engineStart: Upgrade has started. Cannot set the engine address again!
onlyEngine: V2 can only be minted by the upgrade swap engine.
